[SHORT DESC]
Boosts power of Fire-type moves 50% when at 1/3 HP or less. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>When this Pokemon is at 1/3 HP or less, all of its Fire-type moves will have 50% more power.</p>

<h2>Related Abilities</h2>
<p><a href="/dp/abilities/overgrow">Overgrow</a> is a Grass-type equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/abilities/swarm">Swarm</a> is a Bug-type equivalent.<br />
<a href="/dp/abilities/torrent">Torrent</a> is a Water-type equivalent.</p>